title: Tory Shepherd: Hey Malcolm, send in Julie Bishop to deal with Donald Trump | DailyTelegraph
text:
Hey Donald Trump, meet the Minister For Death Stares 
I have a dream. There’s that death stare. (Pic: Kym Smith) 
I have a dream. 
Actually I have many, but I suspect no one’s interested in the one about pork belly and a certain Shia LaBeouf in a cage. 
In this little daydream, Foreign Affairs Minister Julie Bishop shirtfronts US President Donald Trump. Not shirt-front in that hairy-chested Abbott kind of way, but in the blue-eyed death-stare kind of way. 
Pulls him up, swiftly. Julie Bishop would not take any crap from Donald Trump. (Pic: Kym Smith) 
“Grab Her By The Pussy” Trump thinks Australia — steadfast ally, sometimes sycophantic friend — doesn’t matter. He allegedly chucked a tanty during a phone call with Prime Minister Malcolm Turnbull , saying it was “the worst call of the day by far, including Putin”. He accused Australia of trying to export terrorists to the US. 
(The deal on the table actually involves confirmed refugees, currently languishing on Manus Island and Nauru). Other Stories
